title: Is This a Photo of Beto O’Rourke After He Peed His Pants?
subtitle: As far as we know, urinary incontinence has not been a major issue during the U.S. 2020 Democratic presidential debates.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A photograph shows 2020 U.S. Democratic presidential candidate Beto O'Rourke in urine-stained pants.
